## 2.0.0

Add Turn support.
Add prometheus interface.
Use CI, formatting, etc.
Use mix releases instead of distillery.
Move to Cowboy 2.0 and fix user not leaving the room bug.
Use uuids as peer ids.
Use websocket pings and small timeout instead of huge timeout.
Rename option PALAVA_RTC_ADDRESS to SIGNALTOWER_PORT.

## 1.1.0

Fix Websocket timeout bug.
Move to Elixir 1.9.

## 1.0.1

Fix issue that distillery could not stop a running signal tower service.
Introduces new root supervisor that includes supervision for Cowboy.

## 1.0.0

Working state with full palava protocol support.
